        <div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
          <p>Although COD has some solid gameplay, MW2 and Black ops aren’t as good as their predecessors. Not the worst, but definitely way overhyped and overrated.</p>
<p>I’d like to add the new AvP to that list. Was a huuuge disappointment, especially for an avid Aliens fan such as myself. Fortunately, even though it was mainstream, It was not overrated - although the reviews are stupid as hell - they criticized the game for aspects that made it like the movies, i also recall one saying the predator campaign having too much emphasis on stealth. Yeah, a species based on one from a movie where he remains cloaked for almost the ENTIRE MOVIE has too much emphasis on stealth.</p>
<p>Still though, t’was a bitter disappointment.</p>
        </div>

