 Winged One:</div>
<blockquote>
<p>Which is hard to believe since CE was easily one of the most entertaining games I’ve played.  If you said Halo 2 or even Halo 3, I’d at least see how you <span class="bbcode-i">could</span> not enjoy it.</p>
</blockquote>
</aside>
<p>So what you are trying to say is that you have a better taste than me and I should like games that you find entertaining?</p>
<p>Hmm. I think ‘tastes’ don’t work like that. I’ll admit it, I didn’t finish the game, but I played a good portion and although I really wanted to like it, it bored me so much that I ended up uninstalling it.</p>
<p>While it IS true that there are people that are just repeating what other people said to sound cool, you can’t insult EVERYONE who didn’t like it just because you think they are indeed jumping on the bandwagon</p>
